nces\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enter Rodman, who opened the floodgates in a way only she could.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"score\": 0.9999999968567863, \"rank\": 2.783294162215184e-09, \"text\": \"Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floodgates\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Streaking into the box in the 17th minute, Rodman got on the end of a well-weighted pass from Lindsey Horan before flicking the ball behind her to drop two defenders, then turning and striking a low shot behind Zambia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s goalkeeper.\\u00c2 THE USWNT IS OFF AND RUNNING.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"score\": 0.9999999968567863, \"rank\": 2.783294162215184e-09, \"text\": \"Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lindsey Horan\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Horan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the box\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the 17th minute\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"a 