 {\"ngram\": \"the forward line\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This revealed another fundamental truth about Hayes's approach: a commitment to flexibility.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHaving a roster that could adapt is essential.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another fundamental truth\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes's approach\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"a commitment\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"flexibility\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"a roster\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a tight turnaround between games,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes said after naming herOlympic rosterin June.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tight turnaround\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"herOlympic rosterin\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo of course, having players on the roster that could play more than one position mattered with squad depth.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s switches may help preserve players\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 legs in an action-packed Olympic tournament, but her moves also slowed the rhythm to finish out the game.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2984}, {\"ngram\": \"the roster\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"more than one position\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"squad depth.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s switches\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"players\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 legs\", \"